### Context Switcher Interaction

For users who are both a couple AND a vendor, the sidebar header shows a discreet role toggle:

```
┌─────────────────────┐
│  🤍 Wedora          │
│  ┌─────────────────┐│
│  │ 🎉 Wedding Plan ││  ← active (highlighted)
│  │ 🏪 Vendor Panel ││  ← click to switch
│  └─────────────────┘│
├─────────────────────┤
```

This is a **segmented control** at the top of the sidebar — one click switches the entire layout context (routes, sidebar items, page content). Implemented as a simple `navigate('/vendor/dashboard')` or `navigate('/dashboard')`.

