## Shortlisting Flow — Detailed Integration

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Couple as Couple (Browser)
    participant MC as MarketplaceContext
    participant API as marketplaceApi.js
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant AC as AppContext (Vendor Tracker)

    Couple->>MC: Click ❤ Shortlist on VendorCard
    MC->>MC: Optimistically add vendorId to shortlistedIds Set
    MC->>API: shortlistVendor(userId, weddingId, vendorId)
    API->>DB: INSERT into vendor_shortlists
    API->>DB: INSERT into vendors (tracker record)
    DB-->>API: Return { shortlistId, trackerVendorId }
    API->>DB: UPDATE vendor_shortlists.tracker_vendor_id
    API-->>MC: Success
    MC->>AC: dispatch({ type: 'ADD_VENDOR_FROM_MARKETPLACE', payload })
    Note over AC: Vendor Tracker now shows the shortlisted vendor
    
    Couple->>Couple: Navigate to /vendors (My Vendors)
    Note over Couple: Shortlisted vendor appears automatically
```

**Key guarantees:**
1. **No duplication**: `UNIQUE(wedding_id, marketplace_vendor_id)` constraint on `vendor_shortlists`
2. **Real-time sync**: Supabase Realtime channel on `vendor_shortlists` + `vendors` tables
3. **Optimistic UI**: Heart turns filled instantly, DB sync in background
4. **Bi-directional cleanup**: Removing from Vendor Tracker also removes the shortlist bridge record

